                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan>, mit <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>davo<ex>n</ex></expan> cze reden etc.
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>tigen</expan> wöllet. Auch
                            <expan>bitt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir ewr gnade, ob ir <add>von</add>
                        fremden <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> newen lewffe <add>icht</add> west,
                            <add>das</add>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> füglich wer cze
                            <expan>schreib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> czü <expan>embiet<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, daz ir
                        uns das bey dem <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan>
